      <title>霍楚尔领导的纽约民主党人向卡玛拉·哈里斯表示支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/new-york-democrats-led-by-hochul-throw-support-to-kamala-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统乔·拜登退出竞选后不到 24 小时，纽约州民主党人就支持副总统卡马拉·哈里斯成为该党的总统候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/new-york-democrats-led-by-hochul-throw-support-to-kamala-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:59:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界各国领导人纷纷评估哈里斯，为特朗普胜选做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/world-leaders-rush-to-understand-kamala-harris-but-brace-for-a-donald-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯突然成为民主党领跑者，这给美国大选带来了新的不确定性，因为世界各国领导人已经在努力应对唐纳德·特朗普可能重返总统职位的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/world-leaders-rush-to-understand-kamala-harris-but-brace-for-a-donald-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:55:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克向乌克兰提供武器，尽管它并不想这么做</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/slovakia-is-arming-ukraine-even-though-it-doesn-t-want-to</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克国防部长正在推动大幅提高弹药产量。然而，尽管斯洛伐克政府坚决拒绝向乌克兰提供武器，但斯洛伐克制造的炮弹还是流入了乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/slovakia-is-arming-ukraine-even-though-it-doesn-t-want-to</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:27:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉称马杜罗需要学习如何输掉选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-maduro-needs-to-learn-how-to-lose-an-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦警告他的长期盟友尼古拉斯·马杜罗，委内瑞拉的经济未来取决于廉洁的选举，以确保政府在国际社会面前的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-maduro-needs-to-learn-how-to-lose-an-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普利兹克和惠特默支持哈里斯，各州州长纷纷表态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/pritzker-whitmer-get-behind-harris-as-governors-fall-in-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州州长 J.B. Pritzker 和密歇根州的 Gretchen Whitmer 支持卡马拉·哈里斯担任总统，结束了有关她们可能挑战副总统提名的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/pritzker-whitmer-get-behind-harris-as-governors-fall-in-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:15:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>跨山输油管道公司在潜在出售前考虑债务交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/trans-mountain-pipeline-weighs-debt-deal-ahead-of-potential-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在加拿大政府最终出售这家石油管道运营商之前，Trans Mountain Corp. 计划在债券市场借款来为部分未偿还债务进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/trans-mountain-pipeline-weighs-debt-deal-ahead-of-potential-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:05:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出敲响警钟，特朗普交易充满矛盾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-exit-sounds-alarm-on-trump-trades-riven-with-contradiction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街在预测和交易关键选举方面有着糟糕的记录，即使是在最好的情况下也是如此。现在，随着乔·拜登的退出颠覆了美国总统竞选，根据最新的政治头条进行投资的危险性已凸显出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-exit-sounds-alarm-on-trump-trades-riven-with-contradiction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:47:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特勤局局长称特勤局在特朗普集会期间失职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/secret-service-head-says-agency-failed-in-stopping-trump-shooter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一场激烈的国会听证会上，这位陷入困境的特勤局局长表示，她对前总统唐纳德·特朗普遇刺事件的安全漏洞负全部责任，一些议员要求她辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/secret-service-head-says-agency-failed-in-stopping-trump-shooter</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管处于“跛脚鸭”状态，拜登仍希望在海外展现实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-looks-to-project-strength-abroad-despite-lame-duck-status</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登已退出 2024 年总统大选，但他的团队表示，在外交政策方面，他的工作尚未完成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-looks-to-project-strength-abroad-despite-lame-duck-status</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 03:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠特默和摩尔支持竞选，民主党人团结在哈里斯周围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/kamala-harris-endorsements-after-biden-drops-out-of-2024-race-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登退出竞选后，包括摇摆州州长、高级议员以及比尔和希拉里·克林顿在内的著名民主党人迅速支持卡马拉·哈里斯为该党的总统候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/kamala-harris-endorsements-after-biden-drops-out-of-2024-race-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
